<headline>Wind Chill Advisory issued December 06 at 2:07AM MST until December 07 at 11:00AM MST by NWS Glasgow</headline>
<description>...WIND CHILL ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 11 AM MST WEDNESDAY...
...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IS CANCELLED...
* WHAT...Very cold wind chills. Wind chills as low as 30 below
zero.
* WHERE...Northern Valley County.
* WHEN...Until 11 AM MST Wednesday.
* IMPACTS...The cold wind chills could cause frostbite on
exposed skin in as little as 30 minutes.
* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Look for drifting snow at times today and
tonight with slippery roads.</description>
<instruction>Use caution while traveling outside. Wear appropriate clothing, a
hat, and gloves.</instruction>
